data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
Usage:
- Press "W" to open website. Click the manga you want to download, then copy the link and paste into URL.
- Press "List Chapters" to list all the chapter of the manga.
- Select what chapters you need to download and press ">" to add them to download list. Or you can press ">>" to add all.
- Select where to save manga by click "...".
- Finally, press "Start Download" and enjoy.
